CMDI 1.2 toolkit

This toolkit contains the schemata, stylesheets and scripts that form the
basis of CMDI 1.2.

Please be aware of the following:
* Development of the CMDI tookit should happen in ^/metadata/trunk/toolkit
* Changes ready for production should be merged from ^/metadata/trunk 
  to ^/metadata/branches/cmdi-1.2
* Eventually, the sources in the branch will be made available for use in
  production environments.

For more information, see <http://www.clarin.eu/cmdi>.
